# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the general secretary of the mozambican red cross -lrb- <unk> -rrb- , fernanda teixeira , on thursday said that the country 's civil donation to tsunami victims has reached ##,### us dollars .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (o / organization
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Red"
                              :op2 "Cross")
                        :mod (c / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Mozambia")))
                  :ARG2 (s2 / secretary
                        :mod (g / general))))
      :ARG1 (r / reach-01
            :ARG0 (d / donate-01
                  :ARG0 (c2 / country)
                  :ARG2 (p2 / person
                        :ARG1-of (v / victimize-01
                              :ARG0 (t / tsunami)))
                  :mod (c3 / civil))
            :ARG1 (d2 / dollar
                  :mod (p3 / please-01
                        :ARG1 (w / we))))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / thursday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok kosovo 's legislators were sworn into office friday in the first session of a new parliament that is widely expected to declare independence from serbia early this year .
# ::alignments

      :ARG1 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (l / legislate-01)
            :poss (c / city
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Kosovo")))
      :ARG2 (o / office)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :time (s2 / session
            :ord (o2 / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1)
            :part-of (g / government-organization
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Parliament")
                  :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01)
                  :ARG0-of (d2 / declare-02
                        :ARG1 (d3 / depend-01
                              :polarity -
                              :ARG0 (c2 / country
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Serbia"))
                              :ARG1 c2
                              :time (e / early
                                    :op1 (y / year
                                          :mod (t / this))))
                        :ARG1-of (e2 / expect-01
                              :degree (w / wide))))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the story of milton bradley is no longer one of temper tantrums , ill-timed ejections and baseball equipment thrown <unk> and yon .
# ::alignments
(s / story
      :topic (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Milton"
                  :op2 "Bradley"))
      :consist-of (a / and
            :op1 (t / tantrum
                  :mod (t2 / temper))
            :op2 (e / eject-01
                  :ARG1-of (t3 / time-02
                        :ARG1-of (ii / ill-02)))
            :op3 (t4 / throw-01
                  :ARG1 (e2 / equipment
                        :mod (b / baseball)))
            :op4 (e3 / et-cetera))
      :time (n2 / no-longer))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok a british research team has proved that heat can relieve internal pains , such as stomach ache , for up to an hour .
# ::alignments
(p / prove-01
      :ARG0 (t / team
            :mod (r / research-01)
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Britain")))
      :ARG1 (p2 / possible-01
            :ARG1 (r2 / relieve-01
                  :ARG0 (h / heat)
                  :ARG1 (p3 / pain-01
                        :ARG1-of (ii / internal-02)
                        :example (a / ache-01
                              :ARG0 (s / stomach)))
                  :duration (u / up-to
                        :op1 (t2 / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 1
                              :unit (h2 / hour))))))

                                    :mod (j / jersey
                                          :ARG1-of (n / new-01)))

            :ARG0 (g / grow-01
                  :ARG1 (ii / import-01)
                  :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                        :ARG2 (f / fast-02)
                        :ARG3 (m2 / more)
                        :ARG4 (e / export-01))))
      :ARG1-of (s2 / show-01
            :ARG0 (d2 / data
                  :ARG1-of (p / publish-01
                        :ARG0 (o / office
                              :mod (s3 / statistics)
                              :mod (f2 / federal))

                              :weekday (f3 / friday))))))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (r / research-institute
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "National"
                  :op2 "Institute"
                  :op3 "for"
                  :op4 "Demography"
                  :op5 "Studies"))
      :ARG1 (e / exceed-01
            :ARG0 (e2 / expectancy
                  :mod (l / life))
            :ARG1 (y / year)
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1)
            :location (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "France"))
            :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (s2 / study-01
                        :ARG1 (d / demography))))
      :time (w / wednesday))
